<div class="container my-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h1>{{ site.title }}</h1>
            <p>
                {{ site.title }} 2019 will be held on {{ site.enddate }} and is an event by the community, for the
                community. But why not expand this community to give to others? Any profits we make are given back to
                our chosen project.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <h2>Got a talk idea? We want to see it!</h2>
            <p>
                We're pleased to announce our conference, {{ site.title }} should be
                one of the best PHP conferences where community members from around
                the world come together to learn and share information about the latest
                trends and technologies in professional PHP development.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Speaker Package</h2>
            <p>
                Every speaker gets full access to the conference and conference-related events. we don't cover travel
                or hotel by default, but we may be able to arrange something if you need it.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2>Diversity Matters!</h2>
            <p>
                {{ site.title }} is committed to creating a conference that is as inclusive as possible.
                We want to showcase talent available around the Netherlands and welcome international submissions as well.
            </p>
            <p>
                We are also committed to ensuring the conference is a place
                where ideas are exchanged, old friends get together, new friends meet and <strong>harassment
                is not tolerated</strong>. We expect speakers, attendees and sponsor representatives to be
                professional and courteous to each other. We reserve the right to remove, without refund,
                ANY attendee (speaker or otherwise) who is unable to adhere to this policy.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
